4f1b1670cc02e9050c45d4678f3a300050b02f4a.description: Chewed Up is the third concert film and stand-up comedy album by comedian and director Louis C.K. It was filmed and recorded on March 1, 2008 at the Berklee Performance Center in Boston.

41f253d94ced10f87b1452d7511e5924b5d11c16.title: Louis C.K.: Oh My God
41f253d94ced10f87b1452d7511e5924b5d11c16.description: Oh My God" is the fifth full-length comedy special performed by comedian Louis C.K. It premiered on HBO on April 13, 2013. The special was filmed in Phoenix, Arizona at the Celebrity Theatre. The special was nominated for four Emmy awards, winning in the Outstanding Writing For A Variety Special category.

ee4734ce5e49b1f66d33d0c689ded36d74d994cd.title: The Big Lebowski
ee4734ce5e49b1f66d33d0c689ded36d74d994cd.description: From the Academy Award-winning Coen brothers, The Big Lebowski is a hilariously quirky comedy about bowling, a severed toe, White Russians and a guy named...The Dude. Jeff "The Dude" Lebowski doesn't want any drama in his life...heck, he can't even be bothered with a job. But, he must embark on a quest with his bowling buddies after his rug is destroyed in a twisted case of mistaken identity. Starring Jeff Bridges, John Goodman, Julianne Moore, Steve Buscemi, Philip Seymour Hoffman and John Turturro, experience the cultural phenomenon of The Dude in the "#1 cult film of all time!" (The Boston Globe).
